00:00:00,800 --> 00:00:05,120
Food is arguably the best thing about 
being alive. No other bodily pleasure is  

2
00:00:05,120 --> 00:00:10,640
enjoyed multiple times every day and never 
gets old. It is an expression of culture,  

3
00:00:10,640 --> 00:00:14,240
our parents' love and a means 
of celebration or comfort.

4
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:19,280
That’s why it hits a special nerve when we are 
told we should change what and how we eat to  

5
00:00:19,280 --> 00:00:25,280
fight rapid climate change. One of the most 
delicious foods, meat gets the worst press.  

6
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:29,440
It doesn’t help that the topic is really 
hard to properly research yourself  

7
00:00:29,440 --> 00:00:34,320
and debates get emotional quickly. But 
clearly science can give us an answer!

8
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:38,640
The reality is, well, it’s complicated.

9
00:00:38,640 --> 00:00:40,800
Let’s take a look at three 
climate arguments against  

10
00:00:40,800 --> 00:00:43,840
meat that are used a lot and see what happens.

